            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Iuliae <expan><abbr>August</abbr><ex>ae</ex></expan> divi <lb n="2"/>Augusti matri <expan><abbr>Ti</abbr><ex>beri</ex></expan> Cae<lb break="no" n="3"/>saris <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Volusio <lb n="4"/>Saturnino <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ato</ex></expan> pro <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Iulius <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> Sulla ob <expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urionatum</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 5: ob dec. steht auf Rasur. (B): Dubolnić: Z. 3: überflüssige Angabe eines Zeilenfalls nach Aug(usti).</p>
            </div>
